name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForLungCancerAll
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Lung Cancer, All
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to lung cancer.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes non-small cell and small cell lung cancers as well as lung adenoid cystic carcinoma, carcinoid tumors, lymphomas, and sarcomas.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes benign neoplasms, carcinoma in situ, lung neoplasms of uncertain behavior, lung cancer in remission, personal and/or family history of lung cancer, and complications due to lung cancer.)
